metadata.name: Winter Wonderland #1
metadata.description:
Accidentally stumbled into this winter wonderland and was instantly mesmerized by the scene in front of me. This is the best kind of view because it only lasts a short period of time. You know when you visit the same place again, it won't be nearly the same.

This is 1/400th of a second from North Carolina, U.S.A. on January 9th, 2021.

Edition 1/1
